item.title: Hair/MU for Photo Shoot
item.description: 1 day photo shoot, August 15, 2024, 8am to 5pm in Los Angeles area. $200 plus $50 kit fee plus lunch on the day. Cast shoot for promotion purposes, in character. 3 males, one female. Beauty and Hollywood Glam. Possibly some room for creative look if the Director likes your vision. We want two slightly different looks for the female. Female is blond - but the character is ginger. If you can do a temporary color treatment on the day. Send resume, portfolio and contact info to Line Producer at shadowmihai@gmail.com
